                            'PenDenTive' 1.1

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'PenDenTive' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on an 8 by 10 tiles
board in which you try to make alignments of tiles of the same type,
either horizontally or vertically, the more aligments of 3 or more
tiles you make in one move, the more points you get.

